data.description: Discover the epitome of affordable lakeside living in this 3-bedroom, 2-bath townhome at the southern end of Lake Lanier. As a coveted end unit, you'll have all the privacy you are looking for. This townhome has LVP flooring, a fully updated kitchen featuring leathered granite countertops and steel-grey appliances, and freshened baths. The screened porch and deck are perfect for enjoying the serene lakefront scenery. The community dock and nearby boat launch make it a haven for water enthusiasts. Additionally, this townhome is an excellent investment opportunity with the option for 30+ day rentals and is located within the highly regarded Buford City School district.
